{"tid":1679955,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「正能量雞湯」曾經我也想過一了百了","createTime":"2019-10-28T13:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T16:17:02.000Z","uid":114360,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c782b05b108c80989a90b57dcbcdb06940dd2407","tid":1679955,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"致所有身處悲傷邊緣的手足：<br />\n<br />\n細細數來，由炎熱的夏季走到涼爽的秋季，不知不覺已經四個多月。還記得那個暑假，鄺神哭到不能自己的那天，我們失去了一位手足，然後一位、一位、又一位，看著生命的殞落，我們都陷入了難以形容的悲傷。<br />\n<br />\n一次次政府錄音帶式的無情回應，一次次黑警濫捕、濫暴，一次次與家人、朋友的爭吵，不論是和勇，我們都遍體鱗傷，一如梁繼平義士所說， 真正連結香港人的，是痛苦。每個星期六日的街頭，一幕幕衝突在催淚彈中爆發，然後無限輪迴。<br />\n<br />\n隨著夜幕降臨，我們脫下那身黑衣服，看著電視直播那未完待續的一幕幕驚心動魄，新聞裡面彈出的「政府表達嚴厲譴責」，我們都知道，一切還沒有結束。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>太宰治在人間失格中寫道：「我本想這個冬日就死去的，可最近拿到一套鼠灰色細條紋的麻質和服，是適合夏天穿的和服，所以我還是先活到夏天吧」，我不知道黎明什麼時候會來到，但我知道，每個星期六日，總有一群和我一樣不放棄的人走上街頭。所以，請不要那麼快失望、絕望，好嗎？</strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，為大家送上一首中島美嘉的「曾經我也想過一了百了」，希望它能夠在夜深人靜的時候，為你帶來一點點力氣。11月2日，如果你休息夠了，我希望能夠在維園看到你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QL3T2Nzcqcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQL3T2Nzcqcs&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD593lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=dc1ad6ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QL3T2Nzcqcs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後的最後<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCyUTqc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCyUTqc.gif&h=26caf1fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDo not forget, we are always be with you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3d28b79715ec41c3cf8eb114174ecde53bd29b","tid":1679955,"uid":134571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d0bf0647a0be3804f2ce71b0d3761ea3feccae","tid":1679955,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:31:29.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD593lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=3cbc8f74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"cbf653620bdc59fb438f81c680d93e5acbd3efc2","tid":1679955,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:32:17.000Z","msg":"112見"},{"pid":"31ccf1b60368287211a4a4292b57dc041bfffbe7","tid":1679955,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8960a248e74a808a190449f138ef88781f9e5434","tid":1679955,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qytRbgQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqytRbgQ.gif&h=056f04d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a710f147642aca8fec7f164cdbcfb397bd26e5a4","tid":1679955,"uid":50762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"唔開心果陣都會聽呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9678d04350e5d5279f433693e86dc0f918797f","tid":1679955,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"11.2見<br />\n<br />\n我都好鐘意首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701887a7e28cd040236a2d8a7e375e9503066bff","tid":1679955,"uid":331706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply